OL,5, An elderly dementia patient was failed 
OL,6, by the system put in place to protect  
OL,7, Northern Ireland's most vulnerable     
OL,8, adults.                                
OL,10,FStanley O'Neill was not showered for   
OL,11,Fthree months and was found wrapping a  
OL,12,Fcord around his neck.                  
OL,14,FDespite healthcare guidelines, those   
OL,15,Fand other failings were not referred   
OL,16,Ffor adult safeguarding investigations. 
OL,18,FA review also criticised his nursing   
OL,19,Fhome for not being open and transparent
OL,20,Fwith the 79-year-old's family.         
